history.content:
YES YOU WILL BE PLACED AT THE END OF THE WAITLIST! DO NOT DO THE SAME MISTAKE THAT I DID!!!!!!

----

Without the caps lock: yes, there is no way of changing sections without dropping and readding the class. That said, if there is open space in that other section, you can enroll in it directly, or the waitlist for the section may be shorter, so this can still be beneficial.

I am on 186 waitlist and I noticed some sections' waitlists have fewer people. I want to switch sections but the new system does not have the options. I have to add a new Lecture-Disussion combo into my cart and click enroll. If I manage to do this, will I be placed at the very back of the waitlist? Because it makes me feel like I am re-adding the class.
